{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "心地善良的少女与被困的守护龙序章 寻求救援的少女",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "森隐族的村落遭到了帝国的袭击。\\n居住在村落的少女·梅露莎\\n拼了命逃到圣城寻求救援。\\n王子一行人在梅露莎的带领下，\\n出发前往位于森林深处的村落。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "这是……\\n多么可怕的阴谋……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "这样下去可不得了……\\n要想办法告诉她……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "告诉她，不可以来救我！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "尤蒂尔！\\n快去城门那边！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "埃尔菲莉丝？\\n怎么了？那么慌张。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "有位森隐族的少女\\n前来寻求救援！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "听说附近的村落遭到了帝国的镇压，\\n她是从村落逃到这里来的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "什么！？\\n我知道了！马上去！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "尤蒂尔大人！\\n请救救我们的村落！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "少女名叫梅露莎。\\n她所在的村落遭到帝国袭击，\\n转瞬之间便被占领。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "村子很快投降，\\n因此并无多少伤亡\\n便被帝国吞并……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这样啊。\\n没有什么伤亡倒是不幸中的万幸……\\n得尽快制定作战计划夺回村落。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_1001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不过……你不要紧吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "你看起来非常疲惫啊，\\n走路都不太稳……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "没、没事。只是跑来的路上，\\n两天不吃不喝……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "两天！？那可真是够呛。\\n赶快先休息一下吧……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "不用。比起这个，赶快前往村落吧！\\n我来带……路……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "哈啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "咦？这里是……\\n为什么我会睡在床上？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "太好了，你终于醒了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "咦！？尤蒂尔大人！？\\n啊……我想起来了。\\n我来到这里求援，然后……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "不、不能再耽搁了！\\n得赶快回村落……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "啊，你就不要逞强了。\\n等你恢复之后再为我们带路吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我知道你很着急，\\n但既然村落并没有遭到破坏，\\n我们还是从长计议比较好。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_1002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "那我去做出发的准备。\\n希里丝，之后拜托你了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "好的，交给我吧！\\n我刚好拿了食物过来。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "尤蒂尔刚才也说了，\\n好好吃饭，早点恢复吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "是啊……谢谢你，\\n那我就恭敬不如从命了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "啊……请问你叫什么名字？\\n我叫梅露莎。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "我叫希里丝！同为森隐族，\\n今后多多关照啊，梅露莎！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "好、好的……那个，\\n原来希里丝小姐也是森隐族啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "咦！？什、什么！？\\n我的耳朵看起来不像森隐族吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "啊，不、不是这个意思……\\n我只是意外有同族的人在这里。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "我所在的村落，\\n大家基本都不会离开村落……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "啊～嗯，我的村落也是这样。\\n那才是正常的森隐族嘛。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "可是卢卡哥哥……啊，是我哥哥。\\n卢卡哥哥说，\\n村落的这种习俗实在太陈腐。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "于是离开村落成为了王子的伙伴，\\n目前在这座城里生活。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "好、好厉害啊！这种行动力……\\n我一定做不到……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "一点都不厉害。\\n哥哥只是个笨蛋而已。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "一不盯着他，\\n就不知道他会怎么乱来……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "父母都很担心，\\n所以我才来这里看着他。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "希里丝小姐……真是心地善良啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "咦！？不是啦！\\n我才没有！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "而且卢卡哥哥\\n经常说我粗鲁、淘气之类的！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "要说心地善良，\\n我觉得梅露莎才更符合！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "诶……是、是吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "嗯。你为了村落的各位，\\n不眠不休地跑了两天……\\n这可不是常人能做到的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "你说卢卡哥哥厉害，\\n但你也很厉害哦。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "两天……啊！\\n帝国袭击已经过去两天了吗！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "不能再继续休息了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "啊！等等，梅露莎！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "哈啊、哈啊……一跑起来，呼吸就……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "你还不可以动哦。\\n在这里休息一下，然后回房间吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "好、好的……\\n看来是得休息一下……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "梅露莎真的是拼了命地\\n一路跑过来的啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "不过以后我会帮你，\\n有什么事尽管开口哦。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0068",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "谢谢……\\n你的好意我心领了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0069",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "可是总给你们添麻烦，\\n实在过意不去……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0070",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "哎呀，这种事别在意啦。\\n啊！对了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0071",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "我们做朋友吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0072",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "诶？朋、朋友吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0073",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "没错！如果我们是朋友，\\n你就不用那么客气了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0074",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "可、可是……我……\\n我来这里是为了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0075",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "不行吗？我还以为\\n我们能成为好朋友……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0076",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "并不是不行！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0077",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "其、其实我也……\\n希望能和希里丝小姐成为朋友……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0078",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "那就从称呼改起吧！\\n叫我希里丝就行了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0079",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "咦？好、好的……\\n请多指教……希里丝。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0080",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "嗯！请多指教哦！\\n梅露莎！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_01_0081",
